	These sandalwood fragranced Kashmir incense sticks are from the quality Imperial Range which has been created from recipes more than sixty years old so are tried and tested.&nbsp; The ingredients are mixed by hand&nbsp;and the paste is then rolled onto high quality bamboo sticks which then dry naturally in the glorious Indian sunshine.&nbsp; The exotic sandalwood aroma is an ideal way to fill a room with a beautiful but not overpowering aroma.&nbsp; Simply light the tip of the incense stick, carefully blow out the flame and allow the incense to smoulder and fill your room with this beautiful fragrance.</p>
